message.body: Just saw your man in the lib
Aaaaah!!! Hehe! Is he looking tall and happy, as always? Hehe. How was the rest of your weekend?
happy. I'm good. Been working on group project for undergrad class it sucks. What bout you?

Week, group projects with the little ones... I'm good, dropped stuff off at the student life gallery for the 1st show. Too many people opted in for the 2nd, so I offered to show in 1st. I'm kind of psyched though, there is not much stuff, so they wanted all 3 of my pieces. So, I went to Trader Joe's yesterday to pick up cranberry juice... It was so mobbed that I spent $130, and somehow managed to leave without cranberry juice... Story if my life, short term memory loss Cait!
